            "creation_date": 1429471388,
            "body": "<p>Notice the condition of your print :<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>i == 1 ? (\"st\") : ((i==2? \"nd\":i==3? \"rd\":\"th\") + \" number!\")\n           ^                             ^\n         true                          false\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>I added parenthesis to the false part so it is easier for you to understand. <\/p>\n\n<p>I believe what you want is :<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>(i == 1 ? (\"st\") : (i==2? \"nd\":i==3? \"rd\":\"th\")) + \" number!\"\n                                                      ^\n              Now we add it to the result of what is returned for the condition.\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 29734708,
            "question_id": 29734686
        },
        {
