            "last_activity_date": 1429471553,
            "creation_date": 1429471553,
            "body": "<p>You forgot a pair of braces, change:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.println(i==1? (\"st\"):(i==2? \"nd\":i==3? \"rd\":\"th\") + \" number!\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>to:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code> System.out.println((i==1? (\"st\"):(i==2? \"nd\":i==3? \"rd\":\"th\")) + \" number!\");\n                    ^                                         ^\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 29734751,
