            "creation_date": 1429471660,
            "body": "<pre><code>System.out.println(i==1? (\"st\"):(i==2? \"nd\":i==3? \"rd\":\"th\") + \" number!\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>is the source of the problem. Do you see how you have + \" number!\"); after the : that separates the 1st and the 2nd/3rd? You need to have this twice. <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.println(i==1? (\"st number\"):(i==2? \"nd\":i==3? \"rd\":\"th\") + \" number!\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>or <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.println((i==1? (\"st\"):(i==2? \"nd\":i==3? \"rd\":\"th\")) + \" number!\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
